  <chapter id="introduction">
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>
       Etox is a text layout abstraction, built on top of Evas. It is to text,
       what Ebits is to images. It is intended to abstract text layout to
       allow different fonts, colors, styles (outline, shadowed, etc.), word
       wrapping, paragraph layout, columnation and wrapping of text around
       obstacles in the text area.
    </para>
